object.script:
integral = 0 pvOld = 0 out = 0 timer = 0
min = -1 max = 1 minI = -0.5 maxI = 0.5 D = 0
function clamp(x, min, max) return math.max(math.min(x, max), min) end
function onTick() setpoint = input.getNumber(1) pv = input.getNumber(2) sens = input.getNumber(3) trim = input.getNumber(4)*0.01
stab = input.getBool(1)
P = sens*0.5+2 I = sens*0.01+0.05
if setpoint > -0.01 and setpoint < 0.01 then timer = math.min(timer + 1,60) else timer = 0 end
error = setpoint - pv diff = pv - pvOld
if (timer >= 60 or stab) and out < max and out > min then integral = clamp(integral + I*error, minI, maxI) else integral = clamp(integral - 0.1*integral, minI, maxI) end
out = clamp(P*error+integral-D*diff, min, max)
pvOld = pv
output.setNumber(1, out + trim)
end

pvOld = pv
output.setNumber(1, out + trim)
end
